text: The Goat of the world has licked and licked my salted soul until but a candlewick of iron hope remained - but I continue to dip my heart into the sea.
Realised all of this has already happened

I am the puppeteer behind my friends' lives, manipulating them cunningly with the sinister purpose of making them all as happy and successful as possible. All of them are marionettes in my grandiose play, where I also play the role of the audience, cheering them on and helping!
